[[=]]
++ SCP Foundation Site-89
[[/=]]

[[<]]

**Location:** Dallol Woreda, Afar Triangle, Ethiopia

Site-89 is a remote Foundation research site that deals primarily with the containment of historical and religious humanoids and artifacts that benefit from being farther removed from population bases. Located near the East African Great Valley Rift, the highly active geothermal systems throughout Dallol provide effective power for the site and the extreme, inhospitable climate provides further protection from incursion. Director Zala Ababe, Chief of Site Security Gerald Nichols, and Chief of Site Medical Alfred Bernstein are full time staff, but members of Tactical Theology, Parahistory, Archaeology, and other research divisions often cycle through as required.

